{"tid":672594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昏睡司機被警嚇醒　踩油撞救護車","createTime":"2018-05-21T06:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T11:26:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5ebfe24c1ae45e4c0d17c535cfd13f5c161fd6","tid":672594,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:40:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20396874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20396874&d=kmTCRgqU9%2FUFNKzfZ8RYgMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5f47c95a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20396874&h=c9649625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20396874</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月21日 <br />\n<br />\n昏睡司機被警嚇醒　踩油撞救護車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180521/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180521%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=b0fed9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■平治司機被驚醒後突踩油，警員追前拍打車窗要求停車。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】尖沙嘴一名醉爆司機，昨凌晨在停泊了的平治車內伏軚盤入睡，途人以為他病發昏迷，報警求助。警員到場拍窗叫喚，司機突被嚇醒，意亂下未有下車，便踩油開車，結果平治撞向前方救護車車尾，司機受輕傷，警方發現他滿身酒氣，惟事主堅拒接受酒精呼氣測試，最終被捕帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警擬扑窗失手跌警棍<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨零時許，有途人發現一輛白色平治房車停泊於寶勒巷慢線近漆咸道南路邊，車內一名男司機伏在軚盤上久睡不起，恐他病發昏迷，立即報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場後，先召救護車到場，安排車輛沿漆咸道南倒車駛入寶勒巷，泊於平治車前方準備抬走事主送院，兩名警員則拍打車窗嘗試叫喚司機，並打算若對方無反應便敲破車窗救人。大約數十秒後，37歲姓陳男司機突被敲玻璃聲驚醒，但他未有開門接受警員調查，竟踩油開車，平治前駛約6米，撞向救護車車尾，釀成兩車首尾相撞損漽。<br />\n<br />\n有車cam拍攝到事發時一名警員追前拍窗，要求司機停車開門，更怒斥：「你係咪儍咗呀！開門！」然後從腰間取出伸縮警棍戒備，準備扑窗行動時卻一時失手，警棍從手上飛脫跌出街邊，要彎身俯身執回。<br />\n<br />\n陳見多名警員來勢洶洶，終開門下車受查，警方發現陳滿身酒氣，要求他提供酒精呼氣測試樣本遭拒，立即將他拘捕，鎖上手銬。陳事後報稱胸口不適及臉部撞傷，送往醫院檢驗後再帶署調查。<br />\n<br />\n■記者唐家輝  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180521/large/a0803b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180521%2Flarge%2Fa0803b.gif&h=3e71de2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員取出伸縮警棍卻不小心甩手（箭嘴示）。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180521/large/a0803c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180521%2Flarge%2Fa0803c.gif&h=f2dbdeb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■平治撞向救護車車尾損漽，肇事司機（圓圖）被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n上一則<br />\n資方稱開支轉嫁客戶　 恐引發通脹<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n勾結蘭桂坊扒手黨　 便利店員碌卡盜財"},{"pid":"29e2b4d3ff5c3c763aa73e5341805801f16edaf4","tid":672594,"uid":38177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"嗱⋯⋯"},{"pid":"65e3de1d4729c4a970dab680bbd6cfa94b28ec78","tid":672594,"uid":21479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"29e2b4d3ff5c3c763aa73e5341805801f16edaf4","tid":672594,"uid":38177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"嗱⋯⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"香港差佬呢"},{"pid":"7c9db9ea849fc94225447ecf96c34e9863c0de8d","tid":672594,"uid":33147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"On9 vs on9"},{"pid":"5987b3df0bdef67864677e096320d71ebda0fdf6","tid":672594,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:37:57.000Z","msg":"阿sir嚇人唔使你教"},{"pid":"8f7e2953b03e816293d48cc72ccd755dc0ba8a96","tid":672594,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"變埋醉駕？"},{"pid":"9d94648c608d8eead31861e0f95331ce5d05afc0","tid":672594,"uid":174530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f7e2953b03e816293d48cc72ccd755dc0ba8a96","tid":672594,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:38:51.000Z","ms